1953;;All the Brothers Were Valiant;;American;;Richard Thorpe;;Robert Taylor, Stewart Granger, Ann Blyth;;adventure;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/All_the_Brothers_Were_Valiant;;Seafaring saga of two brothers and the woman they both love. Set against South Pacific islands, this love triangle pits the good brother against the bad as they squabble over a woman and a bag of pearls on the floor of a lagoon; the bad brother redeems himself, however, by helping fend off a mutiny.